data.description: ***Multiple Offers Received*** Spacious Bountiful Townhome now available. This is an amazing value for the square footage!  Great layout, 3 beds/2 baths upstairs.   Plenty of room in the basement to add an additional 4th bedroom if needed.  Massive Kitchen! Small quiet community. Amazing location!  Perfect for a commuter.  Super easy access to both north & south bound I15.  Short 15 minute commute to downtown SLC.  Walking distance to Bountiful Rec Center, Meadowbrook Elementary, & Bountiful Jr. High. Shopping, & Entertainment.  Newer Furnace / AC. Tesla Super Charger currently installed and negotiable with the sale. Great potential as a rental property. Clean & Move in ready!  Schedule your private showing today. Feel free to contact the listing agent with any questions.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement. Buyer & Buyer's Agent to verify all listing information.
